name: Proof_319 — Morning Welfare Check (No Egg Output) (2025-12-12, 07:07)
description:
At 07:07 on 2025-12-12, a morning welfare check was conducted on the three remaining ducks at MaMeeFarm.  
No eggs were produced during this cycle. The ducks appeared healthy, active, and stable within the enclosure.

This record documents a verified zero-output event under the DGCP™ continuous proof system, ensuring that absence of production is transparently recorded alongside positive animal welfare conditions.
